    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready to find your next reliable ride? This good-condition vehicle is a fantastic choice for anyone who wants quality without paying mint-condition prices! It's been well cared for and shows only moderate signs of everyday use \u2014 no major issues, drives smoothly, and presents nicely inside and out. A great balance of value and dependability that's ready to hit the road with you!",
      "price": 34000.0,
