    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior has minor surface wear but no significant scratches or dents, with paint that is generally consistent and presentable. The interior shows light use with some small scuffs on surfaces but no major damage to upholstery or components. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained adequately.",
